{"title":"西藏萨迦格言","authors":["王尧选"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西藏萨迦格言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶人有时也会循规蹈矩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不过是他伪装的行动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尽管把玻璃；镀成了宝石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遇见了水会现出原来的颜色。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恶人都要将自己的过失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往别的人身上推诿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乌鸦会把弄脏了的喙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往干净的地上再三地蹭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王尧选译"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}